# Obligation Ledger v1 (clean, minimal)

| ID | Definitions | Assumptions (weakest) | Claim (precise) | Norms / Space | Scale / Limit order |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| O1â€² Microscopic coercivity | Collision operator \(L\), projector \(\Pi=I-P\); dissipation \(D[f]:=-\langle Lf,f\rangle_M\) | Cutoff hard spheres; spectral gap on \(\mathrm{Ran}\,\Pi\); hydrodynamic modes mean-free | \(D[f]\ \ge\ \lambda_{\mathrm{coll}}\ \|\Pi f\|_{\nu,M}^2\) with \(\nu(v)\asymp 1+|v|\) | \(L^2_M\) in \(v\), \(L^2\) in \(x\) with velocity weight | Fixed \(\varepsilon\); near-equilibrium |
| O2 Entropyâ€“energy equivalence | \(F=M(1+f)\), \(H(F\!\mid\!M)=\int M[(1+f)\log(1+f)-f]\), \(E=\|f\|_{L^2_M}^2\) | Small \(f\); positivity \(1+f>0\) | \(\tfrac12 E \le H(F\!\mid\!M) \le 2E\) | \(L^2_M\) vs. relative entropy | Near-equilibrium |
| O3â€² Hypocoercive decay | Mixed energy \(\mathcal E=\|f\|_{L^2_M}^2+\eta_1\langle\nabla_x f,\nabla_v f\rangle_M+\eta_2\|\nabla_x f\|_{L^2_M}^2+\beta\|Pf\|_{H^1_x}^2\) | O1â€², O2, torus PoincarÃ©; nonlinearity small | \(\dot{\mathcal E}\le -\mu\,\mathcal E\) â‡’ \(\mathcal E(t)\le \mathcal E(0)e^{-\mu t}\) | \(H^1_{x,v}\) (with mixed term) | Fixed \(\varepsilon\); block times later |
| O4 Bridge to viscosity | Stress \(S_{ij}=v_iv_j-\tfrac{|v|^2}{3}\delta_{ij}\); cell problem \(LA=-S\) | Invertibility on \(\mathrm{Ran}\,\Pi\); decay of correlations | \(\nu=\tfrac12\langle S,L^{-1}S\rangle=\int_0^\infty\!\langle J(t),J(0)\rangle\,dt>0\) | \(L^2_v\) currents | Kinetic time, then hydrodynamic averaging |
