# One-Block Renewal (plain, annotated)

| Term | Definition | Role in update | Estimate on \(I_n=[t_n,t_{n+1}]\) |
|---|---|---|---|
| Kinetic contraction | \(\theta\,\mathbb h_N(t_n)\) with \(\theta=e^{-\mu\tau_{\mathrm{mix}}}=\tfrac12\) | Shrinks modulated entropy by design | \(\mathbb h_N\) multiplies by \(\tfrac12\) (from O3â€²) |
