âš“ **Fourierâ€“Lyapunov Lift**  

Take Fourier transform in \(x\) (spatial variable):  
\[
\hat{f}(t,\xi,v) = \int_{\mathbb{R}^3} e^{-i x\cdot \xi} f(t,x,v)\,dx .
